name: Warung Beno
address: Jl. Raya Lukluk, Lukluk, Kec. Mengwi, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80351, Indonesia
review 1:
Really good ayam betutu. Chicken cooked in spicy sauce for a few hours. Reasonable prices
If you like Indonesian spicy food this is a must.
review 2: This is view from Warung Beno at the sunset time. Duck with Balinese cuisine that we call Tutu will be your tasty experience of gastronomy. Repeat! Recommended !
review 3: Best ayam betutu in town, the chicken is very delicate and fragrance, the lawar is very good and clear. Very recommended for anyone who looking for best betutu here in Bali.
review 4: The best Ayam Betutu in Bali. It has strong ingredients and spicy enough. Also for the Fried Ayam Betutu, it is awesome! Recommended!
review 5: The place is rather filthy....but honestly, the best ayam betutu you could find in Badung!! Always craving for this dish everytime I go to Bali.
